Diana Hoddinott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diana_Hoddinott 0 Diana Hoddinott (born 1945) is an English actress. She is best known for playing Annie Hacker, the wife of Jim Hacker, in the television comedy serials Yes Minister and Yes, Prime Minister. She also had a role in the historical film, The Gathering Storm, as Mrs Landemare, the Churchills' housekeeper at Chartwell House. Diana_Hoddinott ( born 1945 ) is an_English_actress .
